# IMPORTANT
# This file defines the tracking scope in the NetSuite File Cabinet.
# Do not delete this file, and only modify it when required.
# Changing tracked directories will create a new baseline.
# Changing file extension filters will not.

# Exclude all File Cabinet content by default
/*

# Include SuiteScripts
!/SuiteScripts/**

# Include website and SSP assets
!/Web Site Hosting Files/**

# Include templates
!/Templates/**

# Exclude common document and binary files
**/*.pdf
**/*.doc
**/*.docx
**/*.xls
**/*.xlsx
**/*.ppt
**/*.pptx
**/*.rtf
**/*.zip
**/*.tar
**/*.gz
**/*.tgz
**/*.tbz
**/*.mp3
**/*.mp4
**/*.mov
**/*.mpeg
**/*.mpg
**/*.avi
**/*.bin
